Cabal-Version:          >=1.8
Tested-With:            GHC == 7.4.2, GHC == 7.6.3, GHC == 7.8.4, GHC == 7.10.1, GHC == 7.10.2, GHC == 7.10.3, GHC == 8.0.1, GHC == 8.0.2

Source-Repository head
    Type:         git
    Location:     http://github.com/danfran/cabal-macosx

Library
